2
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:08,640
Deductions take all shapes and styles in every case to be solved.

3
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:10,140
Kogoro's always messing things up

4
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:11,940
but this time he's in a mess, big time!

5
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:13,640
He sees through the one and only truth.

6
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:15,340
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

7
00:00:15,340 --> 00:00:17,640
His name is Detective Conan!

8
00:01:57,290 --> 00:02:03,190
"Kogoro Mouri The Suspect (Part 1)"

9
00:02:14,390 --> 00:02:17,990
Peaches and melons and kumquats.

10
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:19,890
I just love summer fruits.

11
00:02:19,890 --> 00:02:21,390
And they're so ripe.

12
00:02:32,090 --> 00:02:33,090
Ran?

13
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:38,890
Why you...

14
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:42,990
You suggested we spend a night at a hotel since we were coming to Karuizawa

15
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:45,190
to get away from the heat in the city.

16
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:48,090
How come you're the only one who brought swimming trunks!

17
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:51,290
The whole idea was so he could look at girls in the pool, I bet.

18
00:02:51,290 --> 00:02:54,590
Hey come back, I'm not through listening...

19
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:56,090
Too bad!

20
00:02:56,090 --> 00:02:59,190
I'm not lending this to any dirty old man.

21
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:02,190
Besides, mom bought this for me.

22
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:06,190
Hey, wait. Wait up.

23
00:03:07,490 --> 00:03:09,590
"Pool Entrance" -You can't blame me.

24
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:11,590
I've been so busy working lately,

25
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:14,090
the stress has been building up.

26
00:03:14,090 --> 00:03:18,090
But I've been letting you sleep, haven't I?

27
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:22,390
Don't you think you're being unfair to mom?

28
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:25,990
You can't tell what she's doing about now either.

29
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:29,790
She could be going after some young guy...

30
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:40,690
Mom!

31
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:45,690
I don't believe it. What are you doing here?

32
00:03:54,290 --> 00:03:56,290
I just told you.

33
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:57,690
I came to Karuizawa with a lawyer colleague

34
00:03:57,690 --> 00:03:59,890
to do some sightseeing, that's all.

35
00:04:00,890 --> 00:04:03,990
Then what about that neck tie you were buying just now?

36
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:06,290
That... a friend asked me to buy one

37
00:04:06,290 --> 00:04:10,090
and I asked him to help me choose one,

38
00:04:10,090 --> 00:04:11,590
isn't that right?

39
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:14,090
"Norifumi Saku (35)" -Really? I didn't know that.

40
00:04:14,090 --> 00:04:17,190
"Lawyer" -I thought you were buying it for me.

41
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,890
This is no joking matter, Saku.

42
00:04:21,290 --> 00:04:22,790
You're not a little kid,

43
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:24,290
can't you choose one on your own?

44
00:04:24,290 --> 00:04:26,190
Well, excuse me.

45
00:04:27,690 --> 00:04:29,090
Very interesting.

46
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:32,290
Ritsuko.

47
00:04:33,490 --> 00:04:35,190
"Ritsuko Usui (32)" -The great Queen herself

48
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:38,890
"Lawyer" -is reduced to a mere commoner when it comes to her husband.

49
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:40,590
Did she say Queen?

50
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:43,190
Didn't you know?

51
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:47,290
She reigns so mightily in court, no one dares approach.

52
00:04:47,290 --> 00:04:48,790
She's such an eloquent speaker,

53
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:50,590
even judges are left in awe

54
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:53,790
that's why she's been nicknamed Queen of the legal circle.

55
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:55,590
Will you stop saying that?

56
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:58,390
You're the only ones who call me that.

57
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:02,090
"Kenzo Shiozawa (41), Lawyer" -No, I heard some prosecutors say

58
00:05:02,090 --> 00:05:05,790
that when they're in court up against Ms. Kisaki,

59
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:09,290
they feel like traitors defying their Queen.

60
00:05:11,990 --> 00:05:14,690
I think I understand how that feels.

61
00:05:14,690 --> 00:05:17,190
But now the number one female lawyer is you,

62
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:21,090
after you got a ruling in the second trial reversed

63
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:23,190
and took that famous case all the way to the High Court.

64
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:26,590
